\insrsid16008431\charrsid5646288 hem out. We used to get five jam}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 
 deserts for a ha'penny. They was a little - covered with packers chocolate like sealing wax - candle fat they used to be but we used to love it. We used to have - one each - and - sometimes if they were small we'd get - two each, or something
, and then if there was odd one over, we used to give it to the dog. The dog - wasn't our dog, it was the dog downstairs, but it - if it could get up with us and get in ourbed it would. Used to love us, he was old Brick.
