Oh yes, we had parrot and - Trilby, the cat. Trilby. Yes. We - because it always sat with its head on one side and I put a paper cap on it one day, when it was a kitten, so we called it Trilby. Oh yes, we 
cried when that was buried in the garden, it - when - when it died, it was put in a box and -
