 Much better than these kids up in these places. Old Mrs Green lived downstairs and - she used to say - her husband was a train driver, she used to say, you can go down and play in the garden if you sweep it up after you. We used to love that, go down the
re, I know - and she let us have a bonfire down there once, oh we thought that was lovely.
