ce. And - it used to be called Clement Talbot}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16008431\charrsid5646288 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 s.
