Easterand Whitsun. And August Bank Holiday we used to go there. But most times we - my - we used to go to Kensington Gardens, and - my mum'd make up a big - parcel of food, and we'd go and play there and - she'd come up and; take us home but old Aunt
ie Che - Cheetam used to come with us, she used to sit and knit, and - we used to play round her. But we never never never after that attack on me we never - was allowed - anyway I know when -
