\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11557774 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 
No, she used to do - no, we used to buy - fruit was always so cheap. You'd get a pound of cherries for tuppence and - and - penny a pound apples, four pound of potatoes tuppence and pound for three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16008431\charrsid5646288  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 pence, seven cakes for three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16008431\charrsid5646288  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 
pence.
