and turnips and onions. And - barley and beans. All in together, that's what we had. We never had any mucky stuff you get now, tinned stuff. I know only once -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 Was there any tinned stuff around in those days at all?
