\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 Would she do it at the table or from the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11557774 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 No, she used to put the - she used to put - da
d used to carve the meat, and mum used to put the veg - veg on - on our plates, and then we'd - all take our}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16008431\charrsid5646288  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 
plates out and put them in the sink and put the knives and forks in a big j}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16008431\charrsid5646288 ar}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 
 of water, and - then we would - mum would serve up the pudding and we'd eat that and - take - take the plates out again and - mum'd - take the cloth off and shake it and put the coloured cloth on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 When your youngest sisters weren't old enough to eat at the table where would they sit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11557774 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 They had a high chair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 Did you help feed them at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11557774 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 
No, I - I don't think so, no, I - I - I think I used to - I used to give my - little sister - bread and milk, my mother fed all her children, but - herself, but - I used to - I used to give her bread and milk when she wa
s - oh get - getting on, you know, we didn't have all this here - fancy things, now you had bread and milk or porridge, you didn't have a - lot of rubbish. I know when I was ill - and had a bad throat, I - I was only - having bread and milk. But I mean th
e bread - it was bread then, not the - stuff that floats about now.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 Was there any special order you'd be served in?
