ays pass them round, put mum's out - and - was all passed round - you know, anyhow. As long as we got it we didn't care how it was served.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 Would you say that your father was an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11557774 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 Easy per - yes, he - he was very well educat
ed man. To - to my mind, because he could speak several languages, and not only that, he was - his opinions were - his opinions - people used to - we used to listen to him and he used to tell us something and - pass his opinion, and sometimes I'd ask him 
a question, and he would go right from the beginning to tell me. In fact in the end I used to be afraid to ask him something because I had to know the - the origin of it and the end. So -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 Where did he find all these languages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11557774 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 I couldn't tell you my dear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 Did he travel around a lot before he met your mother?
