\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 If you had any problems or worries could you share them with your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11557774 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 
Oh I know if - if anyone of us was ill - I know when my - youngest sister was ill, I had to go - I used to have to read to her, or go and tell her a story, and - I know when she - she was very ill with pneumonia once - 
and we all thought she was going to die, and I can remember my mum and dad sitting up with her, and - I went - in and looked at her and mum and dad were sitting watching her, and I went out and made some tea, and - took it in to my mum and dad. And - I - 
I never forget the look on their faces. 'Cos they thought - my sister and I were asleep. But we - we never - no, we never quarrelled or - never -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 It was a very close warm family really?
\par 
