 - was like us, there was never any quarrels, never any bad words. We were just poor but we had plenty, we didn't - do you know what I mean? We never looked above - we never used to say to ourselves, oh I wish we lived in this and I wish we had that. But 
- unfortunately, my granddaughter - she - has turned all the other way, she - right from a child - we -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 
When you were - you say your parents would never hit you but they would tell you certain things which they expected of you, how would they expect you to behave towards your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11557774 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 
Well, we were always friends, we - sometimes we'd have a fight and - mum would come between us and - just - send us off, but there was never any bad words or anything but - the little - one - the younges
t one, she got very spoilt. Very spoilt she got, because we lost a little sister in between you see, and - she was very spoilt and - and it's never - it's never left her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 Is that Kit?
