\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 What did your parents think about Cissy doing that?
