Oh my - my mother, she - my mother said, oh you shouldn't have hit her. So my father said, I'm very glad she did. So - I got away with that one. And my Sammy - he was home on leave - he - he said - she had a brother Joey, so he said, I'll see that J
oey about her, so he saw Joey and Joey said - oh those two girls, he said. So - he said, well you tell her to leave my sister - my sister alone, he said, and - keep herself to herself. So for a long time after that - I didn't speak to her. But - I never r
eally struck anybody but I did give her a tuppenny one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 What kind of punishment would your parents give you other than physical punishment, what would they do to make you learn a lesson?
