chard, so I'm Susan Annette. Suzie Annette. And only a few weeks ago I said to my little - great-n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16008431\charrsid5646288 i}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 
ece, my prayer book - that was given to me - and it was - all my names in it. I was christened at St James's in Northern Square, because my godmother came from there.
