Well we - I mean we - never had any - occasion to you see mum and dad used to talk - after we'd gone to bed or perhaps they'd talk across the table about something, but nothing t
hat - that - we could interfere with. They - they always had their own business, we never knew what was sorrying them, or - or what wasn't.
