\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 But not in the actual house, you wouldn't have family hymns in the house or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11557774 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 
No, we used to - oh yes, didn't we - we didn't have any music, we - we sang to - we sang to - what my dad started off with. He used to harmonize, we used to sing all those - my - greatest - hymn now, and right from a
 child, The King of Love my Shepherd Is. Oh I think that's - We had a man come - I had a man come round here - a very nicely spoken young man but he came round here about a quarter to ten one night, so he said, I'm doing a survey, he said, of something so
m
ething, he said, can I come in? I said, no you can't. I said if you're doing a survey of anything I said you don't mind doing - asking in the morning I said - no, I'm much too busy. So - he went. But I - what the survey was I don't know. Then I had anothe
r
 letter come, would I - tell them - any complaints I had about - traffic on the road and so forth and so forth and - I said well I - I didn't say I never got out, I said - I don't know much about the traffic now on the road, I said, all I hear is this her
e - passing, I said, buses, fire engines, ambulances. Cars.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 There's a lot more traffic now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11557774 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 
Oh yes, my dear, I can ; I was sitting there one afternoon list 1 summer time, we had a summer last week - last year wasn't it, on a Wednesday I think, an
yway I was sitting by the window - and from teatime - from lunch time 'til - while I was sitting there having me cup of tea I counted four hundred cars. Going both ways you know, and I must - I could have missed some out but I thought to myself, well woul
d
 you believe that. Because I often wondered when - said - thousands of cars a day I thought to myself well how - how could they know, - how can they count them. You - you - I think I'm like my dad. If you asked him anything - you had to sit there and wait
 from the origin to the final, because you'd have to know it all. Didn't say, oh yes and no. It - was started from this and this started from that and - like the mouse}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16008431\charrsid5646288 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 tail on the Rhine, we had to sit there and hear the whole history of that. And of course it was very interesting.
