\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 Were there many books around the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11557774 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 And Bible storeys he used to te
ll us, he used to tell us Bible stories. And - all the parables and - and - Abraham and - and finding Moses in the bulrushes and - the crossing of the Jordan and the - the - the Red Sea rather and - how our Lord - fed - us - with five loaves and two fishe
s and I know my little sister said, cor I bet they didn't half get a little bit each. It had its - it had its funny - sayings with it you know. Oh, poor old dad.
