ouldn't see the sky half the time, I said, and there was millions of birds. So she said - oh yes, so I believe. So she went on with getting the tea. But when dad told us about - spoke about it he said it was a forest and - and - many things happened in th
e forest. And - lots of things that people would never know about - and - birds and - bird watchers were finding different things out about birds a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2700016\charrsid5646288 nd the little animals and squirr}{
