 fourteen or twenty birds by now, he's - he sells them, now I buy tea - and - I get a coupon - a three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2359735\charrsid5646288  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 
