he top shop but one on that side of the road, as you come over the bridge. And - we used to - the shop - the shop was open downstairs, it sold sweets and - biscuits and all sorts of thing, and then our entrance was at the back but our front room and the -
 
and - mum's bedroom looked out into Ladbroke Grove. But ours looked out into Portobello Road. You see? Was right - right up at the top end. And that shop at the end now where all those - what do you call it, the - freezers and all that sort of thing - tha
