d, oh - I wouldn't like that. But - that was my first - talk about the pawn shop. Yes, my - and after - after La}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2359735\charrsid5646288 m}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 
