\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11557774 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 We - we had homework right from - we always had homework, four sums to do - Tue
sdays and Thursdays we had four sums to do, and the next week we used to written essay. And that was the first time - I can remember - that - I had a beautiful book, beautiful prayer book given to me - and they asked me what I would like - would I like a 
b
ook - of - Bible Stories, or would I like a prayer book with my name in it? Well I had this lovely prayer book. And - oh I can see it now my dear, it was in a - in a - it slid into a little case. Was I proud of that. Well - the inspector - we used to have
 inspectors come round the school, and question us. So - he read the essays out that - that we used to write you see in the evening, and so I wrote - I can always remember to this day - the life of a pillar box. And I can remember sa}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
