\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 With Mrs Collier?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11557774 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 And the same with the German family in Westcliffe?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11557774 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 Yes, well it was a sort of a friendly job if you 
know what I mean, it's after I've been so ill you see. And then I went down to Westcliffe, through a friend of Mrs - Madam Collier, I went down to Westcliffe and - she introduced me to the Heikels there name were, Heimphiel, Heimphel, and they lived at St
u
ttgart, he was a very rich man, a very big man and very religious. Oh I was one of the family there my dear, they - and - as we were coming over the bridge - there used to be a butchers cart used to go round, a cart on two wheels, and - like a trap, they 
c
alled it a trap, and the old horse used to go flip-flop and the butchers were Doubles, I remember plainly. Well we saw this right up on the top of the bridge, as we're coming from Holland Park Avenue, I said to my brother, I bet you wouldn't get on that. 
H
e said, I bet I would. He said, I bet you wouldn't. So we both - we both got on that cart and we started it going. We got down to Elvin Crescent, and there used to be a cab rank there, we drove straight into the cab rank - and I was chucked over the - you
 
know, as you go over here there's gardens each side, well I was tossed over in the gardens - and my brother was - was still on the cart, he had a broken arm. I had a - I had a broken nose - I - I could remember having a splint on it. I had a broken nose a
nd a - a fractured knee. That was coming home. And my mother comes - they had me in the hospital. And -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392069 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15806095\charrsid5646288 What did she say to you then?
